Entries.default: "No one to check up on her, I guess."
"Strange. Does no one know that this woman has died, or have the Huana left her here for some reason?"
"Ishi, please don't peck out the eyes."
"Captain, that smell will not wash off without a fight."
"You're not going to ask me to carry that, are you?"
"Is it now your habit to go around collecting corpses? I thought you were content with lost souls."
"That be some booty I'd stop well short of plundering myself, cap."
"Any reason we're taking those? I'm guessing that soul's long gone, huh."
"For what did they just leave her like this?"
